components.html:
Before inspection, check your surroundings and conduct a risk assessment.
Equipment must be isolated against unexpected start-up or movement.
Perform the inspection in the same direction, starting from the same point, each time.
components.label: Content

questions.label: Service / inspection log book up to date
Fuel system (no leaks, fuel cap present)
No unusual noises, vibrations or smells
